ScaffoldWithConfirmation
========================
Extended version of scaffolds.
This scaffold has a confirmation page.


Usage
=====

1. Install plugin.

  ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/usualoma/scaffold_with_confirmation.git

2. Generate model.

  ruby script/generate ModelName [ field ... ]


Example
=======

  ruby script/generate scaffold post
  ruby script/generate scaffold post title:string body:text published:boolean
  ruby script/generate scaffold purchase order_id:integer amount:decimal


